036/586325700ee3f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F586325700ee3f.png&h=458a65dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼這一次與艾瑪華森合作迪士尼真人版電影《美女與野獸》（Beauty and the Beast）的路克伊凡斯，飾演反派「獵人加斯頓」的他在戲外一直以剛硬的帥哥形象聞名，今年他也獲選了世界第 45 帥。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/586325713bed8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F586325713bed8.png&h=9026b660&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼南韓男子團體 EXO 的 22 歲成員 Kai 金鐘仁獲得了 44 名，今年他與知名女團 f(x) 成員 Krystal 宣告成為 2016 演藝圈新情侶檔，簡直是俊男美女的超養眼配對。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/58632572ae06c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F58632572ae06c.png&h=df42c0d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼日本男藝人今年入圍相當稀少，沒想到由前 KAT-TUN 成員赤西仁拿下 31 名，成為今年日本第一帥，也是員赤西仁目前為止的最高名次。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/5863257508a2c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F5863257508a2c.png&h=bdfffcb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼曾經拿下 2014 年冠軍的「霸道總裁」傑米道南（Jamie Dornan），今年獲得了 20 名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/58632578bf20e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F58632578bf20e.png&h=bae1b235&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼全球男人憧憬的時尚模範碧咸，今年拿下了第 17 帥。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/5863257a1e00b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F5863257a1e00b.png&h=e8c9b875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼韓國男團 BIGBANG 的人氣成員 T.O.P 帥氣的臉蛋加上高挑身材，在歐美一直也是韓國帥哥的代表，今年則拿下了 16 名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/5863257b94eb5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F5863257b94eb5.png&h=b6457e82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼同樣正在服役的 Super Junior 始源今年落到了第 12 名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/5863257d69477.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F5863257d69477.png&h=83969d1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼今年與泰勒絲上演了一齣熱戀到分手大戲的英國男演員湯姆&middot;希德斯頓，獲得了第 10 帥的封號。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/5863257f087f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F5863257f087f8.png&h=9a47aeea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼《權力遊戲》男演員基特哈靈頓拿下了第 8 名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/586325803dad3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F586325803dad3.png&h=a710ad7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼台灣男星拿下的最高名次，就是由高以翔獲得了第 7 名！近年來積極轉向美國發展的高以翔，一直都被美國媒體封為是極品亞洲帥哥。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/5863258183930.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F5863258183930.png&h=68eef5b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼他可能是世界最帥的 Gay，39 的麥特&middot;波莫是公認的男神，今年獲得了第 4 名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/58632582cc098.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F58632582cc098.png&h=5aad00b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼BIGBANG 的成員太陽今年大躍進，從去年的第 24 名一口氣竄升到第 2 名，成為了今年的亞洲最帥！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/58632585a156a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F58632585a156a.png&h=98ce10e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼今年的最帥臉孔冠軍就由荷蘭男星米契爾哈斯曼奪下，他在《權力遊戲》第四季接演了 Daario Naharis 這個角色，看過的劇迷肯定就知道他多有魅力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/61036/5863268a43c4b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F61036%2F5863268a43c4b.png&h=a8476aca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"530041e0b0541a6dc9b862390634f73acbe454b6","tid":57741,"uid":545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T12:05:13.000Z","msg":"太陽靚仔過TOP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112f5f397cc27c5617e3c24a5a78f198ca548024","tid":57741,"uid":62201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T12:05:34.000Z","msg":"公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ae835333f5496fba5cd6810fbc5fb10b4a6a7f","tid":57741,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T12:06:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969012eea007c4efe7e700dc2a20608ff9083852","tid":57741,"uid":34424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T12:08:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/y98isr4j\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fy98isr4j&h=24727175&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n93<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ybd31xgz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%